{"tid":2284201,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"記協申請周日千人遊行抗議濫捕記者 警藉詞防疫反對 今午3時舉行上訴聆訊","createTime":"2020-11-13T06:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T10:07:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c4e571946ea1ef9116b4c79f346fa1342890d3ae","tid":2284201,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:14:52.000Z","msg":"報道真相是記者天職。港台《鏗鏘集》編導蔡玉玲透過車牌查冊，追查7.21元朗事件，卻被警方以違反《道路交通條例》拘捕及起訴，新聞自由再受侵害。香港記者協會原定周日（15日）於港島區發起遊行，抗議警方濫捕記者，預計1,000人參與，但被警方以防疫為由反對。記協決定上訴，公眾集會及遊行上訴委員會今午3時舉行聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n記協原定周日中午在港島區發起遊行，抗議警方濫捕記者，並要求在查冊機制中加入傳媒選項，預計1,000人參與。陳朗昇表示，記協執委早前與警方開會，會上警方一直以《公安條例》作為反對理由，但到正式書面通知，則以防疫為由反對。陳指，記協理解有抗疫所需，願意作出多方面配合，包括只限記協會員和新聞系學生參與，參與者需量度體溫及填寫健康申報表等，但都不被接納，故記協決定提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201113/7CZWVEW3SJA25KOT6TXLZEIRDM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201113%2F7CZWVEW3SJA25KOT6TXLZEIRDM%2F&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=32405b47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201113%2F7CZWVEW3SJA25KOT6TXLZEIRDM%2F&h=b244b4ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201113/7CZWVEW3SJA25KOT6TXLZEIRDM/</a>"},{"pid":"d384873c8bd5923c36f8f48414aa3e86ff5b1755","tid":2284201,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830153d88c37320c1f787da1e57d4ce3432c69fc","tid":2284201,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:25:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f209bcedaeb2afe8b9a11e8691e1090648bea6","tid":2284201,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df23abfa2bcd1cd77a3b5fa324001f4533e85b0","tid":2284201,"uid":259520,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:35:38.000Z","msg":"算把!  不過應該個個輪流伸請.<br />\n每次唔發不反對. 都有反對通知書.<br />\n件上法院同post 上網.<br />\n咩野一國兩制.示威遊行自由.<br />\n證實全部九話."},{"pid":"1446829ff98c2afe0e765cd9ceadaf53f6882222","tid":2284201,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2205153f9feee5fcfb7f947e6f0ca732a025d44c","tid":2284201,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:39:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea8167d8846693f964b095c05c5f6423b7bbe96","tid":2284201,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:39:15.000Z","msg":"支持記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0fa3167c6a12926f6dd4e481ecbd08d7db2820","tid":2284201,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:39:28.000Z","msg":"捍衛新聞自由<img src=\"/ass